                            images of saints</p>
                    </decoDesc>
                </physDesc>
                <scribeDesc xmlns="http://www.ilit.bas.bg/repertorium/ns/3.0">
                    <scribe n="1">
                        <locus xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">ff. 1–129</locus>
                        <name xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Daskal Todor Pirdopski</name>
                        <scriptDesc xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">
                            <scriptNote script="Cyrs" style="semiuncial">Late seniuncial</scriptNote>
                        </scriptDesc>
                        <scribeLang>
                            <langNote key="orthography">Without juses, with two jers,
                                inconsistently used</langNote>
                        </scribeLang>
                        <respStmt xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">
